- From above, swarms of invaders ðŸ‘¾ march down aiming to reach your last line of defense.
- Unlease your blazing shots to obliterate the invaders in bursts of glory.
- Victory is yours if you wipe them all out, but if even one invader slips through to the bottom, defeat will be your eternal companion.

# Lessons learned

Building terminal games with it isn't just possible but it's also a great way to explore the framework's capability for fun.
